<span class="n">df_prm</span><span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">df_prm</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">fillna</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">method</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s1">&#39;bfill&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="c1"># 수익률 계산</span>
<span class="n">df_m_ret</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">df_prm</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">pct_change</span><span class="p">()</span>
<span class="c1"># 첫월 수익률 NA이므로 제거</span>
<span class="n">df_m_ret</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">df_m_ret</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">dropna</span><span class="p">()</span>
</pre></div>
